Show HN: Web Bluetooth remote for Canon cameras
text:
Published my Web Bluetooth demo that uses a reverse-engineered protocol of Canon camera remote (BR-E1) to provide a remote intervalometer that works directly from a Web page.

P.S. Yes, as most other Fugu APIs, it works only in desktop and Android Chromium-based browsers.
